Package arcade.agent.helper

Class TissueHelper

java.lang.Object
arcade.agent.helper.TissueHelper
All Implemented Interfaces:
Helper, java.io.Serializable, sim.engine.Steppable
Direct Known Subclasses:
MakeTissueHelper, MoveTissueHelper, RemoveTissueHelper
public abstract class TissueHelper
extends java.lang.Object
implements Helper
Implementation of Helper for time-delayed TissueCell behaviors.

Each TissueHelper object is associated with a specific TissueCell agent. The TissueCell agent calls the scheduleHelper method of TissueHelper to add the behavior to the schedule to be stepped.

Since:
2.2
